OL,3,CInheritance tax change affects 'one
OL,4,Cthird' of NI farms
OL,6,FThe move has caused a considerable
OL,7,Fbacklash from farming and countryside
OL,8,Fcommunities, and led to a dispute over
OL,9,Fjust how many farms and farm
OL,10,Fbusinesses would be affected.
OL,12,FThe National Farmers Union is urging
OL,13,Fthe Government to reverse the move.
OL,15,FSpeaking in the Assembly on Monday
OL,16,Fafternoon, Agriculture Minister Andrew
OL,17,FMuir said the news is causing "real
OL,18,Fconcern" in Northern Ireland.
