OL,3,CInheritance tax change affects 'one
OL,4,Cthird' of NI farms
OL,6,FHe said: "It's impossible to precisely
OL,7,Fdetermine the number of farms affected
OL,8,Fbut around one third would be a
OL,9,Freasonably estimate.
OL,11,F"And much higher within the diary
OL,12,Fsector, at potentially 75%.
OL,14,F"It is going to have a significant
OL,15,Fimpact in Northern Ireland and I'll be
OL,16,Fmeeting the secretary of state today
OL,17,Fand I'll be asking for a rethink in
OL,18,Frelation to this."
