OL,3,CInheritance tax change affects 'one
OL,4,Cthird' of NI farms
OL,6,FChancellor Rachel Reeves told the
OL,7,FBBC's Sunday With Laura Kuenssberg:
OL,8,F"Only a very small number of
OL,9,Fagricultural properties will be
OL,10,Faffected, but last year the benefits
OL,11,Fof agricultural property relief, 40%
OL,12,Fof the benefit was felt by 7% of the
OL,13,Fwealthiest land owners.
OL,15,F"I don't think it is affordable to
OL,16,Fcarry on with a relief like that when
OL,17,Four public finances are under so much
OL,18,Fpressure."
