OL,3,CInheritance tax change affects 'one
OL,4,Cthird' of NI farms
OL,6,FA Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Ministers made clear that the vast
OL,8,Fmajority of those claiming relief will
OL,9,Fnot be affected by these changes. They
OL,10,Fwill be able to pass the family farm
OL,11,Fdown to their children just as
OL,12,Fprevious generations have always done.
OL,14,F"This is a fair and balanced approach
OL,15,Fthat protects the family farm while
OL,16,Falso fixing the public services that
OL,17,Fwe all rely on. We remain committed to
OL,18,Fworking with the NFU and listening to
OL,19,Ffarmers."
